data.description: Opportunity Awaits! NO HOA! A good solid home with one story living on this .71 acre lot with room to grow. Living room with fireplace, a kitchen/dining room combo with builtin hutch. (Some original 1968 charm is still here!)  3 spacious bedrooms with 1.75 baths. Bonus room off the kitchen near the garage, home office/school room/den...you name it!  The possibilities are endless! Fenced backyard with a shed.  Potential for ADU, buyer to verify! Ready for your updates and personal touches. Seller is leaving supplies for some updates for you to complete! You can have animals, a huge garden, play & RV parking and it is on a well & septic. Great Home in a Fantastic location...Tumwater School District also!
